featured_reviews.review_id:
Very Beautiful Mosque .
In this whole area, this mosque looks different and stands out .
This is a very beautiful mosque .
It looks completely Arabian style .
The color of this mosque is also very different .
And the trees outside also look very nice .

If you don't know then let me tell you,
The English word "mosque" denotes a Muslim house of worship . The word evolved from the Arabic term masjid . Masjid is such a place where muslim go for a worship for Allah .

Thanks for reading my review completely
